</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_139" id="68r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschof czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>ges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> hat, daz wir
                                <add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan></add> czwen ausz
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> juden <add>zustunde</add> gen
                                <expan>wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> schicken
                            <expan>sollte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>jude<ex>n</ex></expan> rate besant und den
                                    <add><expan>ernstl<ex>ichen</ex></expan></add>
<expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sich czwen unter in darczu schicken
                                <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan>, also czu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>czekume<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                            <add>Darauff</add> uns der juden rate darauff
                            <expan>czuantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>hat</add>, daz ir kheiner <add>unter in</add> czu der czeit darczu
                        geschickt sey, <add>der</add> czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden kumen
                        müg und <add>wir</add> biten ewr gnade, daz ir uns des darynne niht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>denken</expan> wöllet,
                            <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
